snippet: Malaysian Prime Minister Najib Razak said on Saturday he would meet his Dutch counterpart Mark Rutte next week to discuss how to secure full access for investigators to the site in Ukraine where a Malaysian airliner was downed....

headline.print_headline: Malaysia, Dutch PMs to Discuss Access to Plane Crash Site
headline.main: Malaysia, Dutch PMs to Discuss Access to Plane Crash Site

lead_paragraph: Malaysian Prime Minister Najib Razak said on Saturday he would meet his Dutch counterpart Mark Rutte next week to discuss how to secure full access for investigators to the site in Ukraine where a Malaysian airliner was downed.
